data.description: This home has it all: an incredible layout and an oversized three car garage on a big lot in a great neighborhood! Nicely upgraded and well maintained, this beautiful property features newer appliances, laminate flooring, new backyard landscaping, pavers, and rain gutters, and recently updated SMART home features including new garage door openers, thermostat, and doorbell. This family has loved calling this place home and is excited for you to see it for yourself. Come check it out! This home offers flexible living spaces and bedrooms layouts that can function in a variety of ways based on your family's individual needs. There is a front room that can function as a formal dining room, a home office, workout space, etc.
